{"tid":2432397,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"圍爐熱話● 「城安法」打壓學生 白色恐怖蔓延校園  被退學被DQ 你仲敢上莊？","createTime":"2021-03-04T09:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T09:53:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c9978cb56a680950f0aa323b5687e7a7bc241a55","tid":2432397,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T09:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20210304/HR4JOZS66RGXFOO5XCE5PM5STY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20210304%2FHR4JOZS66RGXFOO5XCE5PM5STY%2F&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv4DCThP5nbHt%2BrJRLkanJ30%3D&h=aa82a80a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fspecial%2F20210304%2FHR4JOZS66RGXFOO5XCE5PM5STY%2F&h=b1d36c2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/special/20210304/HR4JOZS66RGXFOO5XCE5PM5STY/</a><br />\n<br />\n圍爐熱話●<br />\n「城安法」打壓學生 白色恐怖蔓延校園 <br />\n被退學被DQ 你仲敢上莊？<br />\n<br />\n這個年頭，大學生都只可對着電腦上堂，宿舍變得冷清，難以認識新朋友，大學生活失去原有的親密、交流、自由。大學五件事──讀書、住hall、拍拖、上莊、返part-time變得難上加難。「上莊」，即參加學生組織，更是好事多磨，疫症持續、國安法生效，各大學生會今年參選情況慘淡，選上的也要被DQ。大學生們上莊面對甚麼挑戰？上莊的意義為何？上過莊的人又如何看待「老鬼文化」？<br />\n<br />\n我們請來四位曾經或正在上莊的年輕人，包括被指年年「干政」的老鬼Nathan（化名）、。。。。。。。。。。，究竟為何大學生熱衷上莊，有人更故意在學八年只為「照住自己支莊」？<br />\n<br />\n在香港還未槍林彈雨前，大學的校媒記者還是一群希望「拍吓片、玩吓相機」的大學生，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nNathan為何願意在那時候擔大旗，並當上校媒會長？「其實當時都係想做個小。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老鬼無政可干 返校為識朋友<br />\n<br />\n面對今年城大三大莊（學生會幹事會、城大編委、城市廣播）後繼無人，老鬼點睇？Nathan認為城大民意就係唔諗嘢，身邊很多。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nJuno大學一年級玩hall Ocamp時，已經很抗拒hall莊以參加者的容貌氣質將人分類，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有人選擇退莊，亦有人上莊上到延遲畢業，Tamtam就是其中一位。在城大與。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n找郭位被處分 應團結企硬<br />\n<br />\nNat原本認為上莊很無聊，尤其大學的Ocamp以及嗌莊文化，更有很多人指上莊會「爛grade」，但為了達成做記者的夢想，她深思熟慮後認為加入香港文化學會有助起步。<br />\n<br />\n要兼顧學業、事業和莊務，Tamtam笑言是挑戰人體極限，「其實我上第一次莊（城大校媒）時已經畀人炒過，當時做兼職記者⋯⋯因。。。。。。。。。。，「有啲老鬼唔會捨得放手，畢竟係自己有份建立嘅心血。」<br />\n<br />\n城大去年底更新《學生紀律守則》，在第四項不當行為（misconduct）中，校方新增有關「損害大學品牌及形象」的細項，即學生在。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n上莊上到可能「被退學」，幾位莊友點睇？Nathan說：「自己作為老鬼，我個年代冇經歷過咁樣嘅挑戰，我冇資格去話你哋應該點。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/s802s5qSf7jDbSlXwWMl8SKJGeM=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YS5DI2IOUZE3VANFDK4ECA5SU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs802s5qSf7jDbSlXwWMl8SKJGeM%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYS5DI2IOUZE3VANFDK4ECA5SU4.jpg&h=5431badb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNat【城大 香港文化學會】她認為上莊有很大工作量，更大壓力是學生對學會的期望。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/h-rWNXnH9Syj5faDbSHOBnraoO8=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7H57WQKHWZAYVFOHIRRJHFSAVQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh-rWNXnH9Syj5faDbSHOBnraoO8%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7H57WQKHWZAYVFOHIRRJHFSAVQ.jpg&h=d3105fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJuno【某大學 宿生會】quit莊的Juno覺得老鬼的地位不應該超然，上莊的要問清楚自己想要甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dWdEvhTKBBQTFiOr86tef0QAB7g=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3MKU6CYNGVHKBBDO4XELX4ZFAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdWdEvhTKBBQTFiOr86tef0QAB7g%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3MKU6CYNGVHKBBDO4XELX4ZFAM.jpg&h=d4380083&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTamtam【城大 香港文化學會】 上過兩次莊，創立學會後明白為何總有老鬼積極扶助後人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0mTgtWF2xhTVYqUjGwgLVHfeB4Q=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LCFMTCKQYBH7JFSQCAL2UXANHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0mTgtWF2xhTVYqUjGwgLVHfeB4Q%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLCFMTCKQYBH7JFSQCAL2UXANHI.jpg&h=3fb33d29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nNathan 【城大 城市廣播】 身為老鬼，他覺得「城安法」最大的問題是不知道條例可如何延伸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/04ALSG28-WfKECLF-NiUlTMhVVQ=/1082x767/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O7RM4K2WS5CKHLOIZT23IYMXPU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F04ALSG28-WfKECLF-NiUlTMhVVQ%3D%2F1082x767%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO7RM4K2WS5CKHLOIZT23IYMXPU.png&h=fb875b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n城大學生發展處要求《找郭位》MV下架，城大稱毫不知情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/w6JE-JuS5oyAJmCnOYuzcv_6Xuc=/9504x6336/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/W2ZZDC334BFGRMOX4ULRF4SZG4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fw6JE-JuS5oyAJmCnOYuzcv_6Xuc%3D%2F9504x6336%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FW2ZZDC334BFGRMOX4ULRF4SZG4.jpg&h=1bdedff5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大學生會當選內閣「朔夜」請辭，是近期熱話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/liMTO3uy_4AMIX-5PQkNUfOSPJs=/1256x719/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VQPNDRF52FDDHIDRKJBIOLPLUQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FliMTO3uy_4AMIX-5PQkNUfOSPJs%3D%2F1256x719%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVQPNDRF52FDDHIDRKJBIOLPLUQ.png&h=0f031b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n城大學生在Ocamp上dem beat，場面熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0oblnaUu9F4As3uFj_PNPVXOGtg=/4896x3264/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FGFHF4Y66RDCFAURHAU6L3GAH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0oblnaUu9F4As3uFj_PNPVXOGtg%3D%2F4896x3264%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFGFHF4Y66RDCFAURHAU6L3GAH4.jpg&h=bd2a11b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港各大學都有迎新營，但遊戲的程度經常引起不少風波。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：葉楚喬<br />\n<br />\n攝影：魏沛賢"}]}